{"title":"typescript 中通过构造函数的参数直接定义属性","date":"2017-08-23T16:36:31.000Z","author":"许盛","excerpt":"","slug":"typescript中通过构造函数的参数直接定义属性","comments":true,"tags":["typescript"],"categories":["typescript"],"updated":"2018-08-23T09:06:46.487Z","content":"<p><strong>在通常情况下，我们定义一个类时：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight typescript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> Info &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">public</span> name: <span class=\"built_in\">string</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">private</span> age: <span class=\"built_in\">number</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>采用 <code>ts</code> 中简写的语法：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class Info &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tconstructor(</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tpublic name: string</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tprivate age: number ) &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>它可能看上去不像是有属性的类，但它确实有，利用的是 <code>Typescript</code> 提供的简写形式 — 用构造函数的参数直接定义属性。</p>\n<p>这个简写语法做了很多：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>声明了一个构造函数参数及其类型</li>\n<li>声明了一个同名的公共属性</li>\n<li>当我们 new 出该类的一个实例时，把该属性初始化为相应的参数值</li>\n</ul>\n<p>在 <code>ng4</code> 中，就可以通过此种写法来注入服务。</p>\n<p><strong>对比转换前后的代码如下：</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"assets/images/typescript中通过构造函数的参数直接定义属性/diff.png\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"直接从硬盘安装 win10 系统","slug":"直接从硬盘安装win10系统"},"next":{"title":"Rxjs操作符之repeatWhen","slug":"Rxjs操作符之repeatWhen"},"link":"/post/typescript中通过构造函数的参数直接定义属性"}